		Small help:  A context of -1 returns to the next higher one (pop)
			     A context of -2 stays in the current context (no more context="5" within context 5 (this 
                             i ssupported, but should be avoided in new definitions, because you run into problems when using
				-1 than. If a context >=0 is given as the argument a new entry is appended to the stack (push)
